ISLAMABAD, Jun 23 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain has expressed deep grief and sorrow over the demise of the mother of senior TV anchor Javed Iqbal.
In a condolence message, he prayed to Allah Almighty to rest her soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear this loss with fortitude.
